OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FStaying rather cloudy, warm and
OL,6,Fhumid, with periods of rain and some
OL,7,Fheavier and more showery downpours
OL,8,Fpossible during the afternoon, with a
OL,9,Flow risk of thunder. Winds will be
OL,10,Fmoderate and breezy along the coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FRemaining cloudy overnight
OL,13,Fwith rain and showers likely during
OL,14,Fthe evening before easing and turning
OL,15,Fdrier and more settled by the morning.
OL,16,FWinds easing overnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
